			<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/2018/08/23/victim-thinking-van-de-cua-moi-nguoi/" rel="bookmark">Victim thinking &#8211; Vấn đề không của riêng&nbsp;ai</a></h1>			    <!-- BEGIN .entry-meta-header-->
    <div class="entry-meta-header">
        <span class="published"><a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/2018/08/23/victim-thinking-van-de-cua-moi-nguoi/">Tháng Tám 23, 2018</a></span>
    <!-- END .entry-meta-header -->
