<article class="post-4139 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-blog tag-english tag-happiness tag-personal-development" id="post-4139">

		
	
		
		<header class="entry-header">
			<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/2018/04/27/happiness-starts-with-the-definition-of-it/" rel="bookmark">Happiness starts with the definition of&nbsp;it</a></h1>			    <!-- BEGIN .entry-meta-header-->
    <div class="entry-meta-header">
        <span class="published"><a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/2018/04/27/happiness-starts-with-the-definition-of-it/">Tháng Tư 27, 2018</a></span>
    <!-- END .entry-meta-header -->
    </div>
		</header>
		
		    <!-- BEGIN .entry-content -->
    <div class="entry-content">
        <div class="">
<div><img data-attachment-id="4140" data-permalink="https://viethungnguyen.com/2018/04/27/happiness-starts-with-the-definition-of-it/fullsizeoutput_ad23/" data-orig-file="https://viethungnguyen.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/fullsizeoutput_ad23.jpeg?w=580" data-orig-size="4032,3024" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.4&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;iPhone X&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1524743712&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;6&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;16&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0049751243781095&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="fullsizeoutput_ad23" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://viethungnguyen.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/fullsizeoutput_ad23.jpeg?w=580?w=300" data-large-file="https://viethungnguyen.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/fullsizeoutput_ad23.jpeg?w=580?w=580" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4140" src="https://viethungnguyen.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/fullsizeoutput_ad23.jpeg?w=580" alt="fullsizeoutput_ad23.jpeg" srcset="https://viethungnguyen.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/fullsizeoutput_ad23.jpeg?w=580 580w, https://viethungnguyen.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/fullsizeoutput_ad23.jpeg?w=1160 1160w, https://viethungnguyen.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/fullsizeoutput_ad23.jpeg?w=150 150w, https://viethungnguyen.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/fullsizeoutput_ad23.jpeg?w=300 300w, https://viethungnguyen.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/fullsizeoutput_ad23.jpeg?w=768 768w, https://viethungnguyen.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/fullsizeoutput_ad23.jpeg?w=1024 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px"   /></div>
<div></div>
<div class="_1mf _1mj">After starting to viral this question &#8220;<a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/2018/04/25/what-would-make-you-happy-cai-gi-se-lam-ban-hanh-phuc/">What would make you happy?</a>&#8220;, I have received quite many answers on the first day. It&#8217;s very exciting reading all the answers. One young person has responded as below.</div>
<blockquote>
<div class="_1mf _1mj"><em>&#8220;Be, just be, being myself, be a part of this universe&#8230; Just be, nothing more, nothing less&#8230; So then I can experience everything that life can / has to offer.&#8221; </em></div>
<div class="_1mf _1mj"><strong><em>From a young person between 22-30.</em></strong></div>
</blockquote>
</div>
<p>Wonderful, don&#8217;t you agree? Do you have your own answer? If you do, fill in the form as  commitment for your own happiness. There are a few notes here:</p>
<div class="">
<ul>
<li>There is no such right or wrong answer to this question. The answer is for yourself to experience, for your own happiness.</li>
<li class="_1mf _1mj">If you haven&#8217;t had the answer, start searching one for yourself and start stepping on your happiness journey.</li>
<li class="_1mf _1mj">Being able to articulate the answer to this question is really a great step to commit to live up to the values that you think it would bring you happiness. <a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/2018/04/27/happiness-starts-with-the-definition-of-it/#more-4139" class="more-link">Xem chi tiết&#8230;</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
    <!-- END .entry-content -->
    </div>
		    <!-- BEGIN .entry-meta-footer-->
    <footer class="entry-meta-footer">
        <span class="comment-count">Comments: <a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/2018/04/27/happiness-starts-with-the-definition-of-it/#respond">0</a></span>
        <span class="author">Posted by: <a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/author/viethungnguyen/" title="Đăng bởi viethungnguyen" rel="author">viethungnguyen</a></span>
        <span class="entry-categories">Chuyên mục: <a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/category/blog/" rel="category tag">Blog</a></span>
        <span class="entry-tags">Nhãn: <a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/tag/english/" rel="tag">English</a>, <a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/tag/happiness/" rel="tag">Happiness</a>, <a href="https://viethungnguyen.com/tag/personal-development/" rel="tag">Personal Development</a></span>
            <!-- END .entry-meta-footer-->
